        <mxCell id="djyF0K-w9qdzfqEAqw-i-4" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Scenario :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;A2A with Microsoft Agent and Joule Agent for Conversational .User Interface could be MS Teams / Joule. In both the cases, orchestration is handled by Joule&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;MCP server for BDC - There could be 2 approaches : Either BTP SAP-managed / BDC SAP-managed. Based on the final decision, this can be depicted and used.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Joule - MCP Integration - All MCP interactions within SAP has to be initiated from Joule&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Consuming different DPs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;All GenAI via GenAI Hub&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Delta sharing between SAP and Enterprise Databricks instance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=24;absoluteArcSize=1;imageWidth=64;imageHeight=64;strokeWidth=1.5;align=left;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" parent="-ykewXXzDsMCBTA74idt-1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-2232" y="-2550" width="1350" height="193.24" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="djyF0K-w9qdzfqEAqw-i-5" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;What works now :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Joule as entry point&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;A2A with Microsoft&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=24;absoluteArcSize=1;imageWidth=64;imageHeight=64;strokeWidth=1.5;align=left;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" parent="-ykewXXzDsMCBTA74idt-1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-2230.5" y="-2339.24" width="1350" height="193.24" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
